\par\plain {\f0\fs28\b0\i0 Maggie switched shifts with a coworker to attend a play with Evan. After taking the Metra commuter train into downtown Chicago, Maggie debated whether to take a taxi or save money and walk the ten blocks to Evan\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s office. Normally, a ten-block walk would pose no difficulty for Maggie.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs28\b0\i0 She borrowed an outfit from Laura, which included never-before worn designer heels. Maggie\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s under-sized, practically new shoes were the reason for her hesitation to walk. Maggie opted to save the taxi fare and headed on foot toward The Vaughn Group\u8217\'92s office.}}